==离子液体==

甲基吡啶鎓离子的氯化物（''N''-甲基吡啶盐酸盐）在液态是一种[[离子液体|离子液体]]。 几位作者在150 – 200°C（423 – 473 K）的温度范围内表征了甲基吡啶盐酸盐与[[氯化锌|氯化锌]]不同混合物的性能。 <ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Simonis | first1 = L. | last2 = Coppe | first2 = C. | last3 = Glibert | first3 = J. | last4 = Claes | first4 = P. | year = 1986 | title = Properties of mixtures of zinc chloride and N-methylpyridinium chloride in the molten state – I. Phase diagram and heats of mixing | doi = 10.1016/0040-6031(86)85285-6 | journal = Thermochimica Acta | volume = 99 | issue = | pages = 223–232 }}</ref><sup>, </sup><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Claes | first1 = P. | last2 = Simonis | first2 = L. | last3 = Glibert | first3 = J. | year = 1986 | title = Properties of mixtures of zinc chloride and N-methylpyridinium chloride in the molten state – II. Specific mass, electrical conductivity and viscosity | doi = 10.1016/0013-4686(86)87071-2 | journal = Electrochimica Acta | volume = 31 | issue = 12| pages = 1525–1530 }}</ref><sup>, </sup><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Claes | first1 = P. F. | last2 = Coppe | first2 = C. R. | last3 = Simonis | first3 = L. A. | last4 = Glibert | first4 = J. E. | year = 1987 | title = Properties of mixtures of zinc chloride and N-methylpyridinium chloride in the molten state – III. Solubility of hydrogen chloride under atmospheric pressure and comparison with zinc chloride - N-ethylpyridinium bromide mixtures | doi = 10.1021/je00047a020 | journal = Journal of Chemical and Engineering Data | volume = 32 | issue = 1| pages = 70–72 }}</ref><sup>, </sup><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Marković | first1 = R. | last2 = Minić | first2 = D. M. | year = 1997 | title = Conductometric and thermal studies of fused Zn (II) salts containing methyl substituted pyridinium cations | doi = 10.1016/S0254-0584(97)80178-2 | journal = Materials Chemistry and Physics | volume = 50 | issue = 1| pages = 20–24 }}</ref>

